content: What is the name of the jira property for "Request in-person" ? (e.g. how can I search for issues that are marked as in-person?)

"Request in-person" is not EMPTY
e.g.
project = "FHIR Specification Feedback" AND Specification = "SMART Web Messaging (FHIR) [FHIR-smart-web-messaging]" AND "Request in-person" is not EMPTY
Looks like you figured out as I was posting. :)
